Date of Birth: August 24, 1868<br/>
Birthplace: Richmond, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: October 8, 1931<br/>
Death: February 3, 1952<br/>
<br/>
Born Aug. 24, 1868, at Richmond, Cache Co., Utah, to Marriner Wood Merrill and Mariah Loenza Kingsbury.
Ordained apostle Oct. 8, 1931, by Heber J. Grant, at age 63; died Feb. 3, 1952, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 83.